List what set type you want (standard or low serial number), qty desired and forum nameexample:Standard - 5 - MoparMiningLLCLow Serial - 1 - MoparMiningLLCI will be placing the order on 7/21/2022 - after order is confirmed, I will dm everyone with their price.
